<li sourcefile="articles/fin-ops-core/fin-ops/organization-administration/configure-manual-decision-workflow.md" sourcestartlinenumber="63">On the page that appears, click <strong sourcefile="articles/fin-ops-core/fin-ops/organization-administration/configure-manual-decision-workflow.md" sourcestartlinenumber="63">Add</strong>.</li>
<li sourcefile="articles/fin-ops-core/fin-ops/organization-administration/configure-manual-decision-workflow.md" sourcestartlinenumber="64">In the list that appears, select the language that you're entering the text in.</li>
