</li>
<li sourcefile="articles/fin-ops-core/fin-ops/organization-administration/configure-manual-decision-workflow.md" sourcestartlinenumber="69"><p sourcefile="articles/fin-ops-core/fin-ops/organization-administration/configure-manual-decision-workflow.md" sourcestartlinenumber="69">In the <strong sourcefile="articles/fin-ops-core/fin-ops/organization-administration/configure-manual-decision-workflow.md" sourcestartlinenumber="69">Work item instructions</strong> field, enter the instructions.</p>
</li>
<li sourcefile="articles/fin-ops-core/fin-ops/organization-administration/configure-manual-decision-workflow.md" sourcestartlinenumber="70"><p sourcefile="articles/fin-ops-core/fin-ops/organization-administration/configure-manual-decision-workflow.md" sourcestartlinenumber="70">To personalize the instructions, you can insert placeholders. Placeholders are replaced with appropriate data when the instructions are shown to users. Follow these steps to insert a placeholder:</p>
