<h2 id="specify-the-possible-outcomes-of-a-decision" sourcefile="articles/fin-ops-core/fin-ops/organization-administration/configure-manual-decision-workflow.md" sourcestartlinenumber="86">Specify the possible outcomes of a decision</h2>
<p sourcefile="articles/fin-ops-core/fin-ops/organization-administration/configure-manual-decision-workflow.md" sourcestartlinenumber="88">Typically, when a document is assigned to a decision maker, the decision maker is asked a question. The answer to this question is usually <strong sourcefile="articles/fin-ops-core/fin-ops/organization-administration/configure-manual-decision-workflow.md" sourcestartlinenumber="88">Yes</strong> or <strong sourcefile="articles/fin-ops-core/fin-ops/organization-administration/configure-manual-decision-workflow.md" sourcestartlinenumber="88">No</strong>, or <strong sourcefile="articles/fin-ops-core/fin-ops/organization-administration/configure-manual-decision-workflow.md" sourcestartlinenumber="88">True</strong> or <strong sourcefile="articles/fin-ops-core/fin-ops/organization-administration/configure-manual-decision-workflow.md" sourcestartlinenumber="88">False</strong>. Follow these steps to specify the possible outcomes of the manual decision.</p>
<ol sourcefile="articles/fin-ops-core/fin-ops/organization-administration/configure-manual-decision-workflow.md" sourcestartlinenumber="90">
<li sourcefile="articles/fin-ops-core/fin-ops/organization-administration/configure-manual-decision-workflow.md" sourcestartlinenumber="90"><p sourcefile="articles/fin-ops-core/fin-ops/organization-administration/configure-manual-decision-workflow.md" sourcestartlinenumber="90">In the left pane, click <strong sourcefile="articles/fin-ops-core/fin-ops/organization-administration/configure-manual-decision-workflow.md" sourcestartlinenumber="90">Basic Settings</strong>.</p>
</li>
<li sourcefile="articles/fin-ops-core/fin-ops/organization-administration/configure-manual-decision-workflow.md" sourcestartlinenumber="91"><p sourcefile="articles/fin-ops-core/fin-ops/organization-administration/configure-manual-decision-workflow.md" sourcestartlinenumber="91">On the <strong sourcefile="articles/fin-ops-core/fin-ops/organization-administration/configure-manual-decision-workflow.md" sourcestartlinenumber="91">Outcomes</strong> tab, in the <strong sourcefile="articles/fin-ops-core/fin-ops/organization-administration/configure-manual-decision-workflow.md" sourcestartlinenumber="91">Outcome 1</strong> field, enter the name of the outcome, or the option.</p>
</li>
<li sourcefile="articles/fin-ops-core/fin-ops/organization-administration/configure-manual-decision-workflow.md" sourcestartlinenumber="92"><p sourcefile="articles/fin-ops-core/fin-ops/organization-administration/configure-manual-decision-workflow.md" sourcestartlinenumber="92">To add translations of the outcome, follow these steps:</p>
<ol sourcefile="articles/fin-ops-core/fin-ops/organization-administration/configure-manual-decision-workflow.md" sourcestartlinenumber="94">
