<h2 id="specify-when-notifications-are-sent" sourcefile="articles/fin-ops-core/fin-ops/organization-administration/configure-manual-decision-workflow.md" sourcestartlinenumber="109">Specify when notifications are sent</h2>
<p sourcefile="articles/fin-ops-core/fin-ops/organization-administration/configure-manual-decision-workflow.md" sourcestartlinenumber="111">You can send notifications to people when a decision has been made, delegated, or escalated. Follow these steps to specify when notifications are sent, and who the notifications are sent to.</p>
