<li sourcefile="articles/fin-ops-core/fin-ops/organization-administration/configure-manual-decision-workflow.md" sourcestartlinenumber="116"><strong sourcefile="articles/fin-ops-core/fin-ops/organization-administration/configure-manual-decision-workflow.md" sourcestartlinenumber="116">[Choice 1]</strong> – The assigned user has selected <strong sourcefile="articles/fin-ops-core/fin-ops/organization-administration/configure-manual-decision-workflow.md" sourcestartlinenumber="116">[Choice 1]</strong>.</li>
<li sourcefile="articles/fin-ops-core/fin-ops/organization-administration/configure-manual-decision-workflow.md" sourcestartlinenumber="117"><strong sourcefile="articles/fin-ops-core/fin-ops/organization-administration/configure-manual-decision-workflow.md" sourcestartlinenumber="117">[Choice 2]</strong> – The assigned user has selected <strong sourcefile="articles/fin-ops-core/fin-ops/organization-administration/configure-manual-decision-workflow.md" sourcestartlinenumber="117">[Choice 2]</strong>.</li>
<li sourcefile="articles/fin-ops-core/fin-ops/organization-administration/configure-manual-decision-workflow.md" sourcestartlinenumber="118"><strong sourcefile="articles/fin-ops-core/fin-ops/organization-administration/configure-manual-decision-workflow.md" sourcestartlinenumber="118">Delegate</strong> – The assigned user has assigned the decision to another user.</li>
