<h2 id="set-a-time-limit" sourcefile="articles/fin-ops-core/fin-ops/organization-administration/configure-manual-decision-workflow.md" sourcestartlinenumber="345">Set a time limit</h2>
<p sourcefile="articles/fin-ops-core/fin-ops/organization-administration/configure-manual-decision-workflow.md" sourcestartlinenumber="347">Follow these steps if the decision must be made in a specific time.</p>
